<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Juc - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/juc/</link><description>Juc - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/juc/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>JUC并发工具包</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/juc%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/juc%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%85/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="juc并发工具包">JUC并发工具包</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：JUC通过Lock体系替代synchronized提供灵活锁机制，通过Semaphore控制并发数，通过CountDownLatch和CyclicBarrier协调多线程执行节奏，通过CompletableFuture实现异步编排，覆盖了从互斥到协作的完整并发控制场景。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="juc通过显式锁信号量栅栏异步future四类工具提供了比synchronized更精细的并发控制能力">JUC通过显式锁、信号量、栅栏、异步Future四类工具，提供了比synchronized更精细的并发控制能力</h2>
<h3 id="lock体系比synchronized更灵活的锁机制">Lock体系：比synchronized更灵活的锁机制</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>ReentrantLock</th>
          <th>synchronized</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>可中断</td>
          <td>支持lockInterruptibly()</td>
          <td>不支持</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>可超时</td>
          <td>支持tryLock(timeout)</td>
          <td>不支持</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>公平性</td>
          <td>支持公平/非公平模式</td>
          <td>非公平</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>条件变量</td>
          <td>多个Condition</td>
          <td>一个wait/notify</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>尝试获取</td>
          <td>tryLock()</td>
          <td>无</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>性能</td>
          <td>JDK6+优化后接近</td>
          <td>同左</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
